Package di.uniba.ardimento.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Command
    Patter Command: interface that uses a command
    InterfaceTool
    Interface in which the methods that a given tool uses are defined
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CkjmCalculateMetrics
    Class that implements Command, represents the metric calculation command
    CkjmExportMetricsCSV
    Class that implements Command, allows you to export the metrics in CSV format
    CkjmExportMetricsXLS
    Class that implements Command, allows you to export metrics in XLS format
    CkjmExportMetricsXML
    Class that implements Command, allows you to export metrics in XML format
    CkjmTool
    Instance of the abstract class ToolAnalyzer, used to use the CKJM library
    JasomeCalculateMetrics
    Class that implements Command, represents the metric calculation command
    JasomeTool
    Instance of the abstract class ToolAnalyzer, used to use the Jasome script
    ToolAction
    Pattern Command to execute a specific command
    ToolAnalyzer
    ToolAnalyzer represents the abstract class of the tools that will be integrated into the project, each tool has a name and an array of files as default
    ToolFactory
    Factory class to instantiate the various tools that will be used : - CKJM - JASOME
